The paper discusses the use of embedding models for knowledge graph completion, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with issues related to data redundancy and incompleteness, which are relevant to database systems (cs.DB). The task of link prediction is also related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
